pddl.prompt:
You are the orchestrator. Public information:
{environment->public_information}
Participant availabilities:
{diane_availability}
{kelly_availability}
{deborah_availability}
Auditor's cleaned report:
{audit_report}
Global goal:
{agents->orchestrator->goal}
Integrate the inputs and produce a PDDL domain and problem that schedules one 30-minute meeting on Monday such that the chosen time slot is free for all participants per the auditor's cleaned constraints. Target the FastDownwards solver. Enclose the domain in <domain></domain> and the problem in <problem></problem>. If any assumptions are necessary, state them succinctly in comments inside the PDDL problem section.
